WEBVTT

00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:07.820
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:11.989 --> 00:00:17.233
First of all, we have to know what is the truth.

00:00:17.313 --> 00:00:21.452
People are seeking, seeking, seeking all over,

00:00:21.532 --> 00:00:30.232
but they don't know what they are seeking and
what should they get after their seeking.

00:00:33.947 --> 00:00:40.848
This seeking can lead you
into many diverse directions.

00:00:41.607 --> 00:00:47.584
Some of them could be very, very dangerous
and absolutely misleading

00:00:48.653 --> 00:00:54.675
and many must have also felt that way, I'm sure.

00:00:54.755 --> 00:01:02.746
There are many who have found it out but they
think there is no way they can return.

00:01:06.144 --> 00:01:10.172
The seeking is very simple to understand

00:01:10.252 --> 00:01:14.012
that you want to know yourself.

00:01:14.092 --> 00:01:18.867
All the time we say, "I want this, I like this,
'I' this, 'I' that".

00:01:19.492 --> 00:01:24.092
But who is this 'I'? What is it?

00:01:24.609 --> 00:01:31.864
Who is this one, myself? What am I?
Do I know anything about myself?

00:01:32.872 --> 00:01:37.422
It's very superficial knowledge we
have about ourselves.

00:01:37.502 --> 00:01:43.181
Everybody has said, all the religions have said
you should know yourself.

00:01:43.261 --> 00:01:45.394
There's no difference on this point.

00:01:45.474 --> 00:01:49.754
Actually, in all religions, if you go in the
essence there's no difference.

00:01:49.834 --> 00:01:55.481
According to time, it was little bit
stressed on one point

00:01:55.561 --> 00:01:57.632
and sometimes on another point.

00:01:57.712 --> 00:02:04.484
But the fundamental thing is that you have to
know yourself.

00:02:05.208 --> 00:02:08.466
How do you know yourself, is the point.

00:02:09.052 --> 00:02:14.421
People will say do this, give up everything,
give up your family, give up everything,

00:02:14.501 --> 00:02:19.878
wear this kind of dress, cut your hair, or
shave your head – and all that nonsense.

00:02:19.958 --> 00:02:21.958
It's so outward.

00:02:23.032 --> 00:02:27.992
If you put little bit of your intelligence,
you'll see it's all outward.

00:02:28.072 --> 00:02:31.841
It's so skin deep, it has no meaning.

00:02:31.921 --> 00:02:34.606
So, what has to happen?

00:02:35.392 --> 00:02:40.529
We talk of a last breakthrough of the evolution.

00:02:40.609 --> 00:02:43.118
How do you achieve it?

00:02:44.092 --> 00:02:47.626
When you are evolved up to the state of human beings

00:02:48.472 --> 00:02:55.032
we have to know one thing for definitely
that there's something missing within us.

00:02:56.615 --> 00:03:02.431
Otherwise, world would have been the most
beautiful place, the paradise to live in.

00:03:02.511 --> 00:03:06.781
But something wrong with the human beings
and what is that?

00:03:06.861 --> 00:03:13.136
Is to understand how we
have come up through evolution.

00:03:13.216 --> 00:03:20.939
And, as human beings there are so many things
of the animal stage lingering within us.

00:03:21.019 --> 00:03:27.145
The way we talk, the way we try to oppress others,

00:03:27.225 --> 00:03:32.278
the way we talk to sort of dominate others,

00:03:32.358 --> 00:03:38.847
the way we want to snatch everything, the way we
are only worried about our food — this, that.

00:03:38.927 --> 00:03:47.188
All this is not really a noble human beings sides.

00:03:47.754 --> 00:03:51.689
These are all lingering from that animal instinct.

00:03:51.769 --> 00:03:57.295
All right, we have to accept, because we are
human beings, so they are to be there.

00:03:57.375 --> 00:04:03.642
Nothing so much frightening.

00:04:03.722 --> 00:04:07.552
But also we have one more thing: that we think.

00:04:07.632 --> 00:04:12.432
And we think and think and think, and
think no end of ourselves sometimes.

00:04:13.191 --> 00:04:16.664
Sometimes we think we should protest for this.

00:04:16.744 --> 00:04:20.869
Sometimes we feel that we must become very violent.

00:04:20.949 --> 00:04:24.271
All these things are coming from our human mind.

00:04:24.772 --> 00:04:30.247
Animals won't be violent for something
just for violence sake.

00:04:30.327 --> 00:04:32.372
They'll be violent, all right.

00:04:32.452 --> 00:04:36.964
But for their own purpose of
killing some animal or something.

00:04:38.170 --> 00:04:43.489
But here, we have groups and groups
of people who just enjoy violence.

00:04:43.569 --> 00:04:47.210
This is another development in the
human awareness I think,

00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:51.317
that we enjoy destruction of others.

00:04:52.214 --> 00:04:55.403
But also there is a seeking.

00:04:56.212 --> 00:05:01.046
This is the sign that people want their evolution.

00:05:01.126 --> 00:05:04.652
They want to evolve into a better personality;

00:05:04.732 --> 00:05:11.123
that they want to become something
which is complete.

00:05:11.203 --> 00:05:14.258
Now how do you achieve it?

00:05:14.338 --> 00:05:21.244
Now I must say that we have not achieved
our evolution ourselves up to the human level.

00:05:21.324 --> 00:05:25.796
So to achieve a higher awareness

00:05:25.876 --> 00:05:28.924
there must be some arrangement within us.

00:05:29.004 --> 00:05:32.018
And that is the arrangement we are not aware of.

00:05:32.992 --> 00:05:40.696
And that arrangement is that within you is the power.
It's your own power,

00:05:40.776 --> 00:05:47.459
to give you this last breakthrough
through the awakening of that power.

00:05:47.539 --> 00:05:49.818
Already you have been told about it.

00:05:50.969 --> 00:05:53.742
It exists. It is there,

00:05:53.822 --> 00:06:03.072
and it is the right of every human being
to get his self knowledge; self realization.

00:06:03.152 --> 00:06:07.238
'Sahaja': 'saha' means born with you.

00:06:07.318 --> 00:06:09.723
With you is born the right.

00:06:09.803 --> 00:06:14.510
And why should we not ask
under fundamental rights society,

00:06:14.590 --> 00:06:20.567
that we should have our self realization,
which is your own.

00:06:20.647 --> 00:06:23.877
It is there already placed within you.

00:06:23.957 --> 00:06:27.833
You don't have to do anything.
Of course, you can't pay for it.

00:06:27.913 --> 00:06:30.687
How much did you pay for your evolution so far?

00:06:31.446 --> 00:06:34.816
And how can it be different from different people?

00:06:34.896 --> 00:06:41.015
Because in every human being this power,
which we call as Kundalini, exists,

00:06:41.095 --> 00:06:45.880
whether he is white, black, yellow, blue, any color.

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:50.412
Whether he belongs to north or south, anyplace,

00:06:50.492 --> 00:06:53.531
whether he belongs to this country or that country,

00:06:53.611 --> 00:07:01.571
they all have this power universally placed
in their Kundalini.

00:07:01.651 --> 00:07:04.678
Even if I say everybody has a heart,

00:07:04.758 --> 00:07:08.419
so why should we have differentiation?

00:07:08.499 --> 00:07:12.989
But this mind, this human mind
creates this differentiation

00:07:13.069 --> 00:07:19.729
and this problem, saying that, "Of course, they are
not of our country, they don't belong to our group".

00:07:19.809 --> 00:07:24.012
And like animals again we start getting into groups.

00:07:24.092 --> 00:07:27.427
Groups of different

00:07:27.507 --> 00:07:35.174
I don't know the denomination. Like some
people have their fork and spoon put this way.

00:07:35.254 --> 00:07:37.648
So they are one group.

00:07:37.728 --> 00:07:41.815
Some people drink coffee so they have a group.
Like that, you see.

00:07:41.895 --> 00:07:44.012
We are very good at forming groups.

00:07:44.092 --> 00:07:50.492
This is also animal instinct, I think, that
we try to form groups of such stupid things.

00:07:51.243 --> 00:07:56.314
And then we can have wars, because we must fight.

00:07:56.394 --> 00:08:00.841
We are a group, something great,
so we should fight others.

00:08:00.921 --> 00:08:05.689
All these instincts that are
between us are inherited.

00:08:05.769 --> 00:08:09.977
They have come to us. They say it is in our genes.

00:08:10.057 --> 00:08:13.639
Still, can we change the genes?

00:08:14.212 --> 00:08:20.805
Can we transform our personality
into something higher?

00:08:20.885 --> 00:08:24.390
And for that, I tell you, there is a power within us.

00:08:24.470 --> 00:08:27.608
All of you have that power within you.

00:08:27.688 --> 00:08:29.947
And what does it give you?

00:08:30.027 --> 00:08:34.260
It passes through six centres, as told to you.

00:08:34.340 --> 00:08:39.313
It nourishes it, it integrates it,

00:08:39.393 --> 00:08:43.450
and ultimately, it pierces through
the last fontanel bone area.

00:08:43.530 --> 00:08:47.157
We can call that actualization of the baptism

00:08:47.237 --> 00:08:54.133
and is connected to the all-pervading power of
divine love.

00:08:54.213 --> 00:09:00.753
Again I said love: Divine compassion and divine love.

00:09:01.557 --> 00:09:06.693
So you get connected to that power
which is all-pervading.

00:09:06.773 --> 00:09:09.482
If you ask a doctor who runs our heart,

00:09:09.562 --> 00:09:12.151
he'll say it's the autonomous nervous system.

00:09:12.231 --> 00:09:14.672
But what and who is the 'auto'?

00:09:14.752 --> 00:09:18.127
Who does all these things?
Who does all the living works?

00:09:18.207 --> 00:09:20.792
Look at these flowers. Beautiful.

00:09:20.872 --> 00:09:24.812
Who has made these flowers?
Such a different, different flower.

00:09:24.892 --> 00:09:30.332
How does this Mother Earth differentiate
and how she gives all these flowers?

00:09:30.412 --> 00:09:33.770
Do we think about it? We take it for granted.

00:09:33.850 --> 00:09:39.441
All living work we take it for granted,
but it is done by this divine power.

00:09:39.521 --> 00:09:45.332
Believe me, there is this divine power
around us which protects us,

00:09:45.412 --> 00:09:53.272
which looks after us, which guides
us, and also, above all, it loves us.

00:09:54.214 --> 00:09:56.745
And it cares for us.

00:09:56.825 --> 00:10:00.936
It wants that we should all receive

00:10:01.016 --> 00:10:04.285
the blessings of this all-pervading power.